block content
  div.big-space-top
    .container
      .row(class="text-center")
        .col-md-12
          span.text-white
            h1 Welcome to RiiTag!
            br
            p RiiTag is a customizable gamertag for the Wii. By sharing your gamertag (a dynamic image), you can show what you've been playing to your friends! You connect it to a USB Loader, and the tag updates on-the-fly. You need a Discord account in order to start using RiiTag. Covers are provided by GameTDB and this service is developed by RiiConnect24.
            if !user
              a(href="/login" type="button" style="margin-right: 5px;" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Log In
            else
              a(href="/logout" type="button" style="margin-right: 5px;" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Log Out
            a(href="https://wii.guide/riitag" type="button" style="margin-right: 5px;" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Instructions
            br
            img(width="50%" src="/demo" alt="Example")
  script(src='assets/js/jquery.min.js')
  script(src='assets/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js')
